title: Thunder From Above-Air War 1941-1968 (Time Life - Vietnam Exp)
description:
Thunder From Above - Air War 1941-1968 (Time Life - Vietnam Experience)

Boston Publishing Company | 1984 | ISBN 0949526093 | Eng | 200 pages | PDF | 25 MB


This book focuses both on the technology employed during the war and how it was used. It is further enhanced by personal stories from former pilots, which adds much to the overall story. The reader can gain much insight from this book, and it is highly recommended
